  <brief_title>Efficacy of Fibrin Sealant to Reduce the Amount of Post-thyroidectomy Drain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Fibrin Sealant to Reduce the Amount of Postoperative Drain in Patients With Harmonic Scalpel-assisted Total Thyroidectomy With Anterior Compartment Neck Dissections</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
